title: The Fountain of Youth: Five Tibetan Exercises for Rejuvenation
description:
Production year : 1998 Country : USA Genre : Oriental wellness practice Language : English Duration : 37:15



Description : This simple and effective set of exercises, known as the "Five Tibetan Pearls" or "Eye of the Renaissance", is known to many, thanks to the popular book by Peter Kelder and the subsequent development of active threads by others (including Andrew Siderskiy). The practice of "Tibetan pearl" leads to reversing the internal flow of time, the development of personal power, preservation and restoration of health and youthful body. 
practice of "Eye of the Renaissance" is a powerful system of healing, rejuvenation, cleansing and improving the body's energy. Regular performance of rituals 5 can not only restore your health, but also give you new possibilities in terms of spiritual and energy.
